          <description>
            <string language="sv">Så länge atmosfären saknade syrgas, fanns inget ozonskikt. Liv fanns bara under vattenytan.Modul 6 - Livets fiender.Naturkunskap A - Åsö.</string>
            <string language="en">So long the atmosphere lacked syrgas, was no ozone layer. Lives were only during the water surface.

Module 6 - the life's enemies.

Naturkunskap A - Åsö.</string>
          </description>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">So lang ermangelte die Atmosphäre syrgas, war 
keine Ozon-Schicht. Die Leben waren nur während des Wassers 
surface.Module 6 - das enemies.Naturkunskap A der Lebensdauer - Åsö.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Tellement longtemps l'atmosphère a manqué des 
syrgas, n'était aucune couche d'ozone. Les vies étaient 
seulement pendant l'eau surface.Module 6 - l'enemies.Naturkunskap A de
la vie - Åsö.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Assim por muito tempo a atmosfera não faltou 
syrgas, era nenhuma camada de ozônio. As vidas eram somente 
durante a água surface.Module 6 - o enemies.Naturkunskap A da vida - 
Åsö.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Così lungamente l'atmosfera difettava degli 
syrgas, era strato di ozono. Le vite erano soltanto durante 
l'acqua surface.Module 6 - il enemies.Naturkunskap A della vita - 
Åsö.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Τόσο πολύ η ατμόσφαιρα δεν στερήθηκε τα syrgas, 
ήταν κανένα στρώμα όζοντος. Οι ζωές ήταν μόνο κατά τη 
διάρκεια της ενότητας 6 επιφάνειας ύδατος - οι εχθροί 
Naturkunskap Α της ζωής - Εsφ.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">La atmósfera faltó tan de largo syrgas, no era 
ninguna capa de ozono. Las vidas eran solamente durante el agua 
surface.Module 6 - el enemies.Naturkunskap A de la vida - Åsö.</string>
          </description>
